1	SIMPLE	t2	ALL	NULL	NULL	NULL	NULL	1	100.00	Using where
1	SIMPLE	t4	ALL	NULL	NULL	NULL	NULL	1	100.00	Using where; Using join buffer (flat, BNL join)
